<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">今天，校园里又迎来</span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">一群生机勃勃的新鲜面孔</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">他们带着热情和欣喜</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">满怀期待地来到校园</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">让我们一起跟随经管的脚步</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">看看新生们的青春风采</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">今天就为大家带来</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">2024级新生爆照第二弹～</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">新生报道现场</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531480142060267.png" title="1725531480142060267.png" alt="63c86123a9d8722c209495977d8f826.png"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531495723069696.png" title="1725531495723069696.png" alt="84c9cf62099761e85d72079fedcb147.png"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531535917037720.png" title="1725531535917037720.png" alt="37d59731cfd5d15b4dc1cc148736c15.png"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">合影留念</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531955165096303.png" title="1725531955165096303.png" alt="411f18a0bbf29468b09c8538ea08842.png"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531965634072947.png" title="1725531965634072947.png" alt="d1c83f86b0dfcd833b1087cd1194754.png"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">满“新”欢喜，如约而至</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">灼灼芳华，与“新”同行</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">来自五湖四海的2024级新生们</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">遇见，是故事的开始</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">成长，是温暖的篇章</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">未来在经济管理学院</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">我们并肩前行 共赴未来！</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>